about.summary: Models can be improved by post-processing class probabilities, by: recalibration, conversion to hard probabilities, assessment of equivocal zones, and other activities. 'probably' contains tools for conducting these operations.

name: r-probably
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.0.5" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-probably
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/probably_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/probably/probably_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 67006e7797666ea8f808f4c88bc79b033ea4d94c2449242d12a97fa7414f6ad9

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr
    - r-generics
    - r-rlang >=0.4.0
    - r-tidyselect
    - r-vctrs >=0.2.0
    - r-yardstick
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-dplyr
    - r-generics
    - r-rlang >=0.4.0
    - r-tidyselect
    - r-vctrs >=0.2.0
    - r-yardstick

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('probably')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('probably')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/tidymodels/probably/
  license: GPL-2
  summary: "Models can be improved by post-processing class probabilities, by: recalibration, conversion to hard probabilities, assessment of equivocal zones, and other activities. 'probably' contains tools for conducting these operations. "
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - philip-khor
